{"tid":2182691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"化驗師：無發現陳彥霖死前5天內吸食過大麻","createTime":"2020-08-31T12:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T10:04:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"38bcb38ee54c2f0427080355364e75d0519078f7","tid":2182691,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:51:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547022-20200831.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547022-20200831.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0xPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=eeec5837\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547022-20200831.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2299327d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547022-20200831.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n15歲少女陳彥霖的死因研訊第6日，政府化驗所化驗師康祐軒作供說，去年9月26日檢驗死者的肝臟樣本等，進行毒理化驗，但<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">沒有任何發現</span></span></strong>，可以確定陳彥霖死前大約5天內<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">沒有</span></span></strong>吸食過大麻，死前兩天內亦沒有服食過精神科藥物。<br />\n<br />\n當日到場救護隊目莫橋輝作供表示，去年9月22日中午12時許，在西灣河水警基地見到陳彥霖的遺體，手腳全部彊硬，面部和耳後有屍斑，當進一步用心臟去顫器檢查，發現遺體沒有心臟電流活動，證實明顯死亡。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署法醫藍偉文作供說，當日收到警方電話要求他到水警基地，但由於屍體是在海面發現，沒有機會找到環境證據，而且遺體已經被移送到水警基地，現場氣溫高，遺體腐爛機會比較大，因此他沒有到場，而是建議警方盡快將遺體送到殮房保存。陳彥霖的遺體被發現時面部向上，藍偉文說，在一般情況下浮屍是臉部向下，但亦可能因為被海浪沖刷而反轉。<br />\n<br />\n聆訊明天繼續，預料會傳召解剖陳彥霖遺體的醫生和另外兩名化驗專家。"},{"pid":"2c1721ab8223ae2e23f77b1d0cfe68e588b87f2a","tid":2182691,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:51:43.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2dt0hDKK130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2dt0hDKK130&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0xPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=4780fc5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2dt0hDKK130</a>"},{"pid":"31523ecc052de5905c8e79b0590e5d1ee1036a65","tid":2182691,"uid":68689,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:00:17.000Z","msg":"一陣屈埋化驗師食過大麻"},{"pid":"5c7f06e7b785f7f202810f3f8344f03c72ae2675","tid":2182691,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4cbd27201ae9034f892603fbd78bcff5dfbeed1","tid":2182691,"uid":31952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:03:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3b87b4fa0fd953d2b46cecf8f6856c34b7afa23b","tid":2182691,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9003b2b1396e02424009a75e05116404e8eb935c","tid":2182691,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:03:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\"><span clas